That is perfect. Since you are hosting it yourself, all you need is the raw code to drop into your server environment.

You can copy the code below, save it as an `index.html` file, and upload it directly to your hosting provider. It is entirely self-contained, meaning the styling, the interactive notepad, and all 8 clinical cases are bundled into this single block of code.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
